rawContent:
'''Malumac''' was a Zamorakian warrior under [[Skotizo]]'s command. After the battle of [[Carrallangar]] they went to claim an artefact hidden in [[Karamjan Temple|a temple]] deep within the [[Kharazi Jungle]]. Skotizo however betrayed them and although he initially escaped, he was mortally wounded by a trap in his panic. His corpse and [[Malumac's journal|journal]] can be found in a dead end within the cave.
